# Cafe Daily Revenue Analysis

## Overview

This project presents an exploratory analysis of anonymized daily revenue data from a café.

## Dataset

The dataset contains two variables:

- Day
- Revenue

## Objective

The objective of this project is to practice organizing and presenting business data for data analytics projects.

## Tools

- Microsoft Excel

## Data Disclaimer

The dataset has been anonymized for educational and portfolio purposes. Day labels have been used instead of actual dates to protect business confidentiality.
